                " in JEFF-3.3 and ENDF/B-VIII.0) renormalized by the",
                " ratio of the measured cross section to the evaluated",
                " cross section folded by the LiLiT spectrum",
                " (1.02+/-0.02), and multiplied by 2/sqrt(pi).",
                "The LiLIT neutron spectrum was estimated by the",
                " SimLiT-GEANT4 code."
              ]
            }
          ],
